{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-810f4217-1c5f-409c-a8c3-ded0cc778253-12\nfc_c00a0727-64d8-9d36-84ac-68acc61631a1_1","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/createEngineIOPorts.ts"},"result":{"success":{"content":"/**\n\t* 模块名称：本机引擎 IO 装配工厂（骨架）\n\t* 模块说明：按 dataRoot 创建 Memory / Profile / Content / EngineLog Ports。\n\t* Server 边界：仅 app/api、Host 装配、*.server.ts、utils/server 可引用；\n\t* 禁止 Client（pageComponents / bis / stores / typeFiles / ajaxProxy 等）任何 import。\n\t* 实现迁入节奏见里程碑 V2-IO-4～V2-IO-7；本文件在 V2-IO-3 仅占位，避免误用未迁完的装配。\n\t*/\nimport type {\n\tContentPort,\n\tEngineLogPort,\n\tMemoryPort,\n\tProfilePort,\n} from \"@airpc/rpg-engine\";\n\n/** 本机 Studio 注入 Host 的四 Port 套件（技术设计 23）。 */\nexport type EngineIOPorts = {\n\tmemory: MemoryPort;\n\tprofile: ProfilePort;\n\tcontent: ContentPort;\n\tengineLog: EngineLogPort;\n};\n\n/**\n\t* 创建指向 `dataRoot` 的本机 Ports。\n\t* V2-IO-3 骨架阶段尚未迁入实现；调用方须等 V2-IO-4+ 完成后再装配生产 Host。\n\t*\n\t* @param _dataRoot 工作区根（本机即仓库 `data/` 或等价绝对路径）\n\t*/\nexport function createEngineIOPorts(_dataRoot: string): EngineIOPorts {\n\tthrow new Error(\n\t\t\"createEngineIOPorts：IO 实现尚未迁入 engineIOModule（见里程碑 V2-IO-4+）\",\n\t);\n}\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":34,"fileSize":1191,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/engineIOModule/createEngineIOPorts.ts","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":34},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-810f4217-1c5f-409c-a8c3-ded0cc778253-12\nfc_c00a0727-64d8-9d36-84ac-68acc61631a1_1","startedAtMs":"1784781602087","completedAtMs":"1784781602945"},"model_call_id":"13c061d1-bf77-4f24-9332-8c1ca31f861a-3-ecp1","session_id":"01baa976-9ca0-4238-822f-22f39680caba","timestamp_ms":1784781602930}
